#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:35
#, no-c-format
msgid "Window Specific Settings: Quick Start"
msgstr "Akende spetsiifilised seadistused: kiirtutvustus"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:41
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Please note that this configuration will not take effect if you do not use "
"&kwin; as your window manager. If you do use a different window manager, "
"please refer to its documentation for how to customize window behavior."
msgstr ""
"Pane tähele, et siinsetel seadistustel ei ole mingit mõju, kui sa ei kasuta "
"KDE enda aknahaldurit &kwin;. Kui kasutusel on mõni muu aknahaldur, siis "
"vaata palun selle dokumentatsioonist, kuidas akende käitumist kohandada."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:47
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Many of the settings you can configure here are those you can configure on a "
"global basis in the <guilabel>Window Behavior</guilabel> &systemsettings; "
"module, however some of them are even more detailed."
msgstr ""
"Suuremat osa sellest, mida siin seadistada saab, saab globaalselt seadistada "
"Süsteemi seadistuste moodulis <guilabel>Akende käitumine</guilabel>, kuid "
"teatud asju on siin võimalik veelgi täpsemalt häälestada."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:51
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"They encompass geometry, placement, whether a window should be kept above or "
"below others, focus stealing prevention, and translucency settings."
msgstr ""
"Seadistuste hulka kuuluvad akende geomeetria ja asetuse määramine, "
"otsustamine, kas hoida aken teiste peal või all, fookuse röövimise vältimine "
"ning läbipaistvusega seotud seadistused."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can access this module in two ways: from the titlebar of the application "
"you wish to configure, or from the &systemsettings;. If you start it from "
"within &systemsettings; you can use the <guibutton>New...</guibutton> to "
"create a window profile, and the <guibutton>Detect Window Properties</"
"guibutton> button on the resulting dialog to partially fill in the required "
"information for the application you wish to configure."
msgstr ""
"Mooduli saab avada kahel moel: selle rakenduse tiitliribalt, mida soovid "
"seadistada, või Süsteemi seadistustes. Süsteemi seadistustes käivitatuna "
"saab nupule <guibutton>Uus...</guibutton> klõpsates luua aknaprofiili ning "
"seejärel näeb nupule <guibutton>Tuvasta</guibutton> klõpsates dialoogi, kus "
"leiab juba teatud info akna kohta, mida soovid seadistada."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:63
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also at any time <guibutton>Modify...</guibutton> or "
"<guibutton>Delete</guibutton> any stored settings profile, and reorder the "
"list. Reordering the list using the <guibutton>Move Up</guibutton> and "
"<guibutton>Move Down</guibutton> buttons effects on how they are applied."
msgstr ""
"Kõigi salvestatud seadistusprofiilide puhul võib kasutada nuppe "
"<guibutton>Muuda...</guibutton> ja <guibutton>Kustuta</guibutton>, mis "
"teevad just seda, mida nende nimetus ütleb. Samuti võib profiilide nimekirja "
"elementide järjekorda muuta nuppudega <guibutton>Liiguta üles</guibutton> ja "
"<guibutton>Liiguta alla</guibutton>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid "Overview"
msgstr "Ülevaade"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kwin; allows the end-user to define rules to alter an application's window "
"attributes."
msgstr ""
"&kwin; võimaldab kasutajal määrata kindlaks reeglid, millega saab muuta "
"rakendus akna atribuute."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For example, when an application is started, it can be forced to always run "
"on <emphasis>Virtual Desktop 2</emphasis>. Or a defect in an application can "
"be worked-around to force the window above others."
msgstr ""
"Näiteks võib panna rakenduse käivitumisel alati töötama "
"<emphasis>virtuaalsel töölaual 2</emphasis>. Samuti võib näiteks saada üle "
"rakenduse puudujäägist ja sundida akna alati paiknema teiste peal."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Step-by-step <link linkend=\"examples\">examples</link> are provided along "
"with detailed information on using the <link linkend=\"kwin-rule-editor"
"\">&kwin; Rule Editor</link> to specify <link linkend=\"window-matching"
"\">Window Matching</link> and <link linkend=\"window-attributes\">Window "
"Attributes</link>."
msgstr ""
"Käsiraamat pakub põhjalikke <link linkend=\"examples\">näiteid</link> ning "
"üksikasjalikku teavet, kuidas kasutada  <link linkend=\"kwin-rule-editor"
"\">&kwin;i reeglite redaktori</link> <link linkend=\"window-matching\">akna "
"sobivuse</link> ja <link linkend=\"window-attributes\">akna attibuutide</"
"link> määramiseks."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid "Examples and Application Workaround"
msgstr "Näited ja rakenduse puudujääkide korvamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To see what's possible, detailed <link linkend=\"examples\">examples</link> "
"are provided which can also be used to model your own rules."
msgstr ""
"Nägemaks, mis on üldse võimalik, sisaldab käsiraamat <link linkend=\"examples"
"\">näiteid</link>, mida võib võtta eeskujuks omaenda reeglite "
"väljatöötamiseks."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:83
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "A special page is to dedicated to address <link linkend=\"application-"
#| "workarounds\">Application Workaround</link>."
msgid ""
"A special page is dedicated to address <link linkend=\"application-"
"workarounds\">Application Workaround</link>."
msgstr ""
"Spetsiaalne lõik on pühendatud <link linkend=\"application-workarounds"
"\">rakenduse puudujääkide</link> ületamisele."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid "KWin Rule Editor"
msgstr "KWini reeglite redaktor"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid "Invoking the KWin Rule Editor"
msgstr "KWini reeglite redaktori avamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:101
#, no-c-format
msgid "There are several ways to invoke the &kwin; Rule Editor. Below are two:"
msgstr ""
"&kwin;i reeglite redaktorit saab avada mitmel moel, toome siin 'ra kaks "
"võimalust:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Right-click on the title-bar of any window, choose <menuchoice><guimenu>More "
"Actions</guimenu><guimenuitem>Window Manager Settings...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> and in the <guilabel>Configure</guilabel> window, select "
"<guilabel>Window Rules</guilabel> or"
msgstr ""
"Tee paremklõps suvalise akna tiitliribal, vali <menuchoice><guimenu>Rohkem "
"toiminguid</guimenu><guimenuitem>Aknahalduri seadistused...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> ja <guilabel>seadistamise</guilabel> aknas <guilabel>Akna "
"reeglid</guilabel> või"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>System Settings</guimenu><guisubmenu>Window Behavior</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Window Rules</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Süsteemi seadistused</guimenu><guisubmenu>Akende käitumine</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Akna reeglid</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:109
#, no-c-format
msgid "The main window is used to:"
msgstr "Peaaknas saab:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Affect rules with <guilabel>New...</guilabel>, <guilabel>Modify...</"
"guilabel> and <guilabel>Delete</guilabel>"
msgstr ""
"Mõjutada reegleid käskudega <guilabel>Uus...</guilabel>, <guilabel>Muuda...</"
"guilabel> ja <guilabel>Kustuta</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Share rules with others via <guilabel>Import</guilabel> and "
"<guilabel>Export</guilabel>"
msgstr ""
"Jagada reegleid teistega käskudega <guilabel>Impordi</guilabel> ja "
"<guilabel>Expordi</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:114
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Ensure desired <link linkend=\"rule-evaluation\">rule evaluation</link> "
"using <guilabel>Move Up</guilabel> and <guilabel>Move Down</guilabel>"
msgstr ""
"Kindlustada soovitud <link linkend=\"rule-evaluation\">reegli hindamine</"
"link> käskudega <guilabel>Liiguta üles</guilabel> ja <guilabel>Liiguta alla</"
"guilabel>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:116
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rule Evaluation"
msgstr "Reegli hindamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:117
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When an application starts (or the rules are modified), &kwin; evaluates the "
"rules from the top of the list to the bottom. For all rules which match a "
"window, the collective set of attributes are applied to the window, then the "
"window is displayed."
msgstr ""
"Kui rakendus käivitatakse (või reegleid muudetakse), hindab &kwin; reegleid "
"nimekirja algusest lõpuni. Kõigi reeglite korral, mis sobivad aknaga, "
"rakendatakse aknale kõik atribuudid ja siis avatakse aken."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:119
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Should two or more matching rules enable the same attribute, the setting in "
"the <emphasis>first</emphasis> rule in the list is used."
msgstr ""
"Kui sama atribuuti peaksid rakendama kaks või rohkem sobivat reeglit, "
"kasutatakse reeglit, mis on nimekirjas <emphasis>eespool</emphasis>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can tailor children windows for the application by placing the more "
"restrictive rules first - see the <link linkend=\"application-on-all-"
"desktops-and-handle-one-child-window-uniquely\">Kopete and Kopete Chat "
"Window</link> example."
msgstr ""
"Rakenduse alamaknaid saab samuti omaette kohendada, seades piiravamad "
"reeglid ettepoole - vaata näidet <link linkend=\"application-on-all-desktops-"
"and-handle-one-child-window-uniquely\">Kopete ja Kopete vestlusaken</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:125
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rule Editor"
msgstr "Reeglite redaktor"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:139
#, no-c-format
msgid "The editor is composed of four tabs:"
msgstr "Redaktor koosneb neljast kaardist:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:142
#, no-c-format
msgid "Window matching"
msgstr "Akende sobivus"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:143 index.docbook:256
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Size &amp; Position</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Suurus ja asukoht</guilabel>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:144 index.docbook:257
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Arrangement &amp; Access</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Paigutus ja ligipääs</guilabel>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:145 index.docbook:258
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Appearance &amp; Fixes</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Välimus ja parandused</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:147
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As the name implies, <guilabel>Window matching</guilabel> is used to specify "
"criteria to match one or more windows. The other three tabs are used to "
"alter the attributes of the matching windows."
msgstr ""
"Nagu nimigi ütleb, saab kaardil <guilabel>Akende sobivus</guilabel> määrata "
"kriteeriume, millele üks või enam akent peavad vastama. Ülejäänud kolmel "
"kaardil saab muuta sobivate akende atribuute."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:149
#, no-c-format
msgid "Panels can also be affected."
msgstr "Samuti saab mõjutada paneele."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:151 index.docbook:162
#, no-c-format
msgid "Window Matching"
msgstr "Akende sobivus"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:152
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each window rule has user specified <link linkend=\"window-matching\">Window "
"Matching</link> criteria. &kwin; uses the criteria to determine whether the "
"rule is applicable for an application."
msgstr ""
"Igal akna reeglil on kasutaja määratud <link linkend=\"window-matching"
"\">akna sobivuse</link> kriteeriumid. &kwin; kasutab neid kriteeriume "
"määramaks, kas reeglit tuleb rakendusele rakendada või mitte."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:155 index.docbook:239
#, no-c-format
msgid "Window Attributes"
msgstr "Akna atribuudid"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:156
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Along with Window Matching criteria, each window rule has a set of <link "
"linkend=\"window-attributes\">Window Attributes</link>. The attributes "
"override the corresponding application's settings and are applied before the "
"window is displayed by &kwin;."
msgstr ""
"Lisaks akna sobivuse kriteeriumidele on igal akna reeglil teatav hulk <link "
"linkend=\"window-attributes\">akna atribuute</link>. Atribuudid tühistavad "
"vastava rakenduse seadistused ja neid rakendatakse, enne kui &kwin; akent "
"näitab."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Window Matching</guilabel> tab is used to specify the criteria "
"&kwin; uses to evaluate whether the rule is applicable for a given window."
msgstr ""
"Kaardil <guilabel>Akna sobivus</guilabel> saab määrata kriteeriumid, mida "
"&kwin; kasutab hindamaks, kas reeglit tuleb konkreetsele aknale rakendada "
"või mitte."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:178
#, no-c-format
msgid "Zero (match any window) or more of the following may be specified:"
msgstr ""
"Määrata võib null (sobib iga aken) või rohkem järgmistest kriteeriumidest:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:181
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Window class (application)</guilabel> - match the class."
msgstr "<guilabel>Akna klass (rakendus)</guilabel> - sobib klass."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:182
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Match whole window class</guilabel> - include matching the "
"secondary class."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Kogu akna klassi sobivus</guilabel> - sobib ka sejundaarklass."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Window role</guilabel> - restrict the match to the function of the "
"window (&eg; a <emphasis>main window</emphasis>, a <emphasis>chat window</"
"emphasis>, &etc;)"
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Akna roll</guilabel> - sobivust piiratakse akna funktsiooniga "
"(näiteks <emphasis>peaaken</emphasis>, <emphasis>vestlusaken</emphasis> "
"jne.)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:186
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Window types</guilabel> - restrict the match to the type of "
"window: <guilabel>Normal Window</guilabel>, <guilabel>Dialog Window</"
"guilabel>, &etc;"
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Akna tüübid</guilabel> - sobivust piiratakse akna tüübiga: "
"<guilabel>Tavaline aken</guilabel>, <guilabel>Dialoogiaken</guilabel> jne."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:187
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Window title</guilabel> - restrict the match to the title of the "
"window."
msgstr "<guilabel>Akna tiitel</guilabel> - piirab sobivust akna tiitliga."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:188
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Machine (hostname)</guilabel> - restrict the match to the host "
"name associated with the window."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Masin (masinanimi)</guilabel> - piiratakse sobivust aknaga seotud "
"masinanimega."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:190
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"While it's possible to manually enter the above information, the preferred "
"method is to use the <guilabel>Detect Window Properties</guilabel> button."
msgstr ""
"Võimalik on küll ka kogu see teave käsitsi sisestada, aga eelistatud meetod "
"on siiski kasutada nuppu <guilabel>Akna omaduste tuvastamine</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:192
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For each field, the following operators can be applied against the field "
"value:"
msgstr ""
"Kõigi väljade puhul saab välja väärtuse juures kasutada järgmisi operande:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:195
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Unimportant</guilabel> - ignore the field."
msgstr "<guilabel>Ebaoluline</guilabel> - välja eiratakse."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:196
#, no-c-format
msgid "Exact Match"
msgstr "Täpne sobivus"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:197
#, no-c-format
msgid "Substring Match"
msgstr "Alamstringi sobivus"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:199
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Both <guilabel>Exact Match</guilabel> and <guilabel>Substring Match</"
"guilabel> implement case insensitive matching. For example, <emphasis>AB</"
"emphasis> matches the string <emphasis>AB</emphasis>, <emphasis>ab</"
"emphasis>, <emphasis>Ab</emphasis> and <emphasis>aB</emphasis>."
msgstr ""
"Ei <guilabel>täpse sobivuse</guilabel> ega <guilabel>alamstringi sobivuse</"
"guilabel> korral arvestata tähesuurusega. Näiteks <emphasis>AB</emphasis> "
"vasteks on nii string <emphasis>AB</emphasis>, <emphasis>ab</emphasis>, "
"<emphasis>Ab</emphasis> kui ka <emphasis>aB</emphasis>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:202
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "<guilabel>Regular Expression</guilabel> - Qt's regular expressions are "
#| "implemented - see <ulink url=\"http://qt-project.org/doc/qt-4.8/qregexp."
#| "html\">pattern matching using regular expressions</ulink>."
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Regular Expression</guilabel> - Qt's regular expressions are "
"implemented - see <ulink url=\"https://doc.qt.io/qt-5/qregexp.html\">pattern "
"matching using regular expressions</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Regulaaravaldis</guilabel> - kasutatakse Qt regulaaravaldisi, "
"vaata ingliskeelset seletust <ulink url=\"http://qt-project.org/doc/qt-4.8/"
"qregexp.html\">pattern matching using regular expressions</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:204
#, no-c-format
msgid "Detect Window Properties"
msgstr "Akna omaduste tuvastamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:218
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Detect Window Properties</guilabel> function simplifies the "
"process of entering the matching-criteria."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Akna omaduste tuvastamise</guilabel> funktsioon lihtsustab "
"sobivuse kriteeriumide sisestamist."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:221
#, no-c-format
msgid "For the application you'd like to create a rule, start the application."
msgstr "Kui soovid luua mõnele rakendusele reegli, käivita see rakendus."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:222
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Next, in the <guilabel>Window matching</guilabel> tab, set the number of "
"seconds of delay before the <guilabel>Detect Window Properties</guilabel> "
"function starts. The default is zero seconds."
msgstr ""
"Seejärel määra kaardil <guilabel>Akende sobivus</guilabel> sekundite arv, "
"mis oodatakse enne <guilabel>akna omaduste tuvastamise</guilabel> "
"funktsiooni käivitamist. Vaikimisi väärtuseks on null sekundit."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:223
