msgstr ""
"Kui aken soovib fookust, saab skaalal <guilabel>Puudub</guilabel> kuni "
"<guilabel>Äärmuslik</guilabel> määrata, kas tunnistada seda soovi ja seada "
"aken kõigi teiste kohale või soovi eirata (mis võib jätta akna teiste taha):"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:454
#, no-c-format
msgid "None - Always grant focus to the window."
msgstr "Puudub - aknale antakse alati fookus."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:455
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Low</para>"
msgstr "<para>Madal</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:456
#, no-c-format
msgid "Normal"
msgstr "Tavaline"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:457
#, no-c-format
msgid "High"
msgstr "Kõrge"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:458
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Extreme - The window's focus request is denied. Focus is only granted by "
"explicitly requesting via the mousing."
msgstr ""
"Äärmuslik - akna fookusesoovi eiratakse. Fookus antakse aknale ainult siis, "
"kui seda spetsiaalselt hiirega soovitakse."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:464
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"See <guilabel>Accept focus</guilabel> to make a window read-only - not "
"accept any keyboard input."
msgstr ""
"Vaata <guilabel>fookuse aktsepteerimist</guilabel> muutmaks akent "
"kirjutuskaitstuks, et see ei võtaks vastu mingit klaviatuurisisendit."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:467
#, no-c-format
msgid "Accept focus"
msgstr "Fookuse aktsepteerimine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:469
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Toggle whether the window accepts keyboard input. Make the window read-only."
msgstr ""
"Võimaldab lülitada, kas aken tunnistab klaviatuurisisendit. Selle abil saab "
"muuta akna kirjutuskaitstuks."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:472
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ignore global shortcuts"
msgstr "Globaalsete kiirklahvide eiramine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:474
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Toggle whether to ignore global shortcuts (as defined by "
#| "<menuchoice><guimenu>System Settings</guimenu><guisubmenu>Shortcuts and "
#| "Gestures</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Global Shortcuts</guimenuitem></"
#| "menuchoice> or by running <varname>kcmshell5 keys</varname> in "
#| "<guilabel>konsole</guilabel>) while the window is active."
msgid ""
"Toggle whether to ignore global shortcuts (as defined by "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>System Settings</guimenu><guisubmenu>Shortcuts and "
"Gestures</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Global Shortcuts</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> or by running <varname>kcmshell6 keys</varname> in "
"<guilabel>konsole</guilabel>) while the window is active."
msgstr ""
"Võimaldab määrata, kas eirata globaalseid kiirklahve (nagu need määrab "
"kindlaks <menuchoice><guimenu>Süsteemi seadistused</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Kiirklahvid ja žestid</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Globaalsed kiirklahvid</guimenuitem></menuchoice> "
"või <varname>kcmshell5 keys</varname> käivitamine <guilabel>Konsoolis</"
"guilabel>), ku aken on aktiivne."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:477
#, no-c-format
msgid "Closeable"
msgstr "Suletav"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:479
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Toggle whether to display the <guilabel>Close</guilabel> button on the title "
"bar."
msgstr ""
"Võimaldab määrata, kas tiitliribal näidatakse nuppu <guilabel>Sulge</"
"guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:483
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A terminal window may still be closed by the end user by ending the shell "
"session however using <guilabel>Accept focus</guilabel> to disable keyboard "
"input will make it more difficult to close the window."
msgstr ""
"Terminaliakent saab kasutaja sellest hoolimata sulgeda shelliseanssi "
"lõpetades, aga <guilabel>fookuse aktsepteerimise</guilabel> kasutamine "
"klaviatuurisisendi keelamiseks muudab akna sulgemise juba palju "
"keerulisemaks."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:486
#, no-c-format
msgid "<emphasis role=\"bold\">Window type</emphasis>"
msgstr "<emphasis role=\"bold\">Akna tüüp</emphasis>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:488
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Change the window to another type and inherit the characteristics of that "
"window:"
msgstr "Võimaldab muuta akna tüüpi ja pärida selle akna tunnused:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:490
#, no-c-format
msgid "Normal Window"
msgstr "Tavaline aken"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:491
#, no-c-format
msgid "Dialog Window"
msgstr "Dialoogiaken"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:492
#, no-c-format
msgid "Utility Window"
msgstr "Utiliidi aken"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:493
#, no-c-format
msgid "Dock (panel)"
msgstr "Dokk (paneel)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:494
#, no-c-format
msgid "Toolbar"
msgstr "Tööriistariba"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:495
#, no-c-format
msgid "Torn-Off Menu"
msgstr "Eraldatud menüü"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:496
#, no-c-format
msgid "Splash Screen"
msgstr "Käivitusekraan"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:497
#, no-c-format
msgid "Desktop"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:498
#, no-c-format
msgid "Standalone Menubar"
msgstr "Eraldi menüüriba"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:499
#, no-c-format
msgid "On Screen Display"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:505
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use with care because unwanted results may be introduced. For example, a "
"<guilabel>Splash Screen</guilabel> is a automatically closed by &kwin; when "
"clicked."
msgstr ""
"Kasuta seda ettevaatlikult, sest see võib kaasa tuua soovimatuid tagajärgi. "
"Näiteks suleb &kwin; automaatselt <guilabel>käivitusekraani</guilabel>, kui "
"sellele klõpsata."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:508
#, no-c-format
msgid "Block compositing"
msgstr "Komposiidi blokeerimine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:510
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Toggle whether to disable compositing while the window <emphasis>exists</"
"emphasis>. If compositing is enabled and the rule specifies to disable "
"compositing, while <emphasis>any</emphasis> matching window exists, "
"compositing will be disabled. Compositing is re-enabled when the last "
"matching window terminates."
msgstr ""
"Võimaldab määrata, kas blokeerida komposiit, kui aken <emphasis>on olemas</"
"emphasis>. Kui komposiit on sisse lülitatud ja reegel selle keelab, siis "
"keelatakse see juhul, kui on olemas <emphasis>ükski</emphasis> sobiv aken. "
"Komposiit lülitatakse uuesti sisse, kui viimane sobiv aken töö lõpetab."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:517
#, no-c-format
msgid "Examples"
msgstr "Näited"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:518
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The first example details all the necessary steps to create the rules. In "
"order to keep this page a manageable size, subsequent examples only list "
"steps specific to the example."
msgstr ""
"Esimene näide toob ära kõik reegli loomiseks vajalikud sammud. Et osa oleks "
"vähegi mõistliku suurusega, on järgnevate näidete juures toodud ära ainult "
"näitele omased sammud."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:520
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Pager</guilabel> attribute refers to the <guilabel>Virtual "
"Desktop Manager</guilabel>:"
msgstr ""
"Atribuut <guilabel>Töölaua vahetaja</guilabel> tähistab "
"<guilabel>virtuaalsete töölaudade haldurit</guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:533
#, no-c-format
msgid "Pin a Window to a Desktop and set other Attributes"
msgstr "Akna kinnistamine töölauale ja teiste atribuutide määramine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:534
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Pin &akregator; to <emphasis>Virtual Desktop 2</emphasis>. Additionally, "
"start the application with a preferred size and position. For each "
"attribute, use the <guilabel>Apply Initially</guilabel> <link linkend="
"\"parameters\">parameter</link> so it can be overridden at run-time."
msgstr ""
"Kinnistame &akregator;i <emphasis>virtuaalsele töölauale 2</emphasis>. "
"Lisaks käivitame rakenduse kindla suuruse ja asukohaga. Kasutame iga "
"atribuudi korral <link linkend=\"parameters\">parameetrit</link> "
"<guilabel>Rakendatakse algselt</guilabel>, et seda oleks võimalik töö ajal "
"tühistada."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:536
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &kwin; rule is created as follows:"
msgstr "&kwin;i reegel tuleb luua järgmiselt:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:539
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Start &akregator; on <emphasis>desktop two</emphasis>, size and position it "
"to suit:"
msgstr ""
"Käivita &akregator; <emphasis>töölaual 2</emphasis> ning aseta see sinna, "
"kuhu vaja, suurusega, mida vaja:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:551
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Right-click on the titlebar and select <menuchoice><guimenu>More Actions</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Window Manager Settings...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>:"
msgstr ""
"Tee paremklõps suvalise akna tiitliribal ja vali <menuchoice><guimenu>Rohkem "
"toiminguid</guimenu><guimenuitem>Aknahalduri seadistused...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:563
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select the <guilabel>Window Rules</guilabel> in the left column and click on "
"<guilabel>New...</guilabel>:"
msgstr ""
"Vali vasakul <guilabel>Akna reeglid</guilabel> ja klõpsa nupule "
"<guilabel>Uus...</guilabel>:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:575
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Edit Window-Specific Settings</guilabel> window is displayed. "
"<guilabel>Window matching</guilabel> is the default tab:"
msgstr ""
"Ilmub aken <guilabel>Akende spetsiifiliste seadistuste muutmine</guilabel>. "
"Vaikimisi on avatud kaart <guilabel>Akende sobivus</guilabel>:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:587
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click <guilabel>Detect Window Properties</guilabel> with <guilabel>0s delay</"
"guilabel> the cursor immediately turns into cross-hairs. Click (anywhere) "
"inside the &akregator; window (but not the title bar). The window criteria "
"are presented. Match only by primary class name so leave the check boxes "
"unchecked - for additional information see <link linkend=\"window-matching"
"\">window matching</link>:"
msgstr ""
"Klõpsa nupule <guilabel>Akna omaduste tuvastamine</guilabel>, nii et "
"viivitus oleks <guilabel>0s</guilabel>, mille korral kursor võtab kohe risti "
"kuju. Klõpsa kuskil &akregator;i aknas (aga mitte tiitliribal). Näed akna "
"kriteeriume. Valime sobivuse ainult primaarklassi järgi, nii et jäta "
"kastikesed märkimata (vaata täpsemalt osast <link linkend=\"window-matching"
"\">akende sobivus</link>):"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:599
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking <guilabel>OK</guilabel> the previous window back-fills the results "
"in the <guilabel>Window Matching</guilabel> tab. Enter a meaningful text in "
"the <guilabel>Description</guilabel> field (which is displayed in the "
"<guilabel>KWin Rule</guilabel> window):"
msgstr ""
"Klõpsuga nupule <guilabel>OK</guilabel> täidetakse suletud akna põhjal "
"andmed kaardil <guilabel>Akende sobivus</guilabel>. Kirjuta mingi mõistlik "
"tekst väljale <guilabel>Kirjeldus</guilabel> (seda näidatakse "
"<guilabel>KWini reeglite</guilabel> aknas):"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:611
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enable the window attributes: <guilabel>Position</guilabel>, <guilabel>Size</"
"guilabel> and <guilabel>Desktop</guilabel>. The initial values are set by "
"<guilabel>Detect Window Properties</guilabel> and can be overridden:"
msgstr ""
"Lülita sisse akna atribuudid <guilabel>Asukoht</guilabel>, <guilabel>Suurus</"
"guilabel> ja <guilabel>Töölaud</guilabel>. Esialgsed väärtused on määratud "
"<guilabel>akna omaduste tuvastamise</guilabel> põhjal, aga neid saab "
"vajaduse korral muuta:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:623
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking <guilabel>OK</guilabel> in the previous window returns to the main "
"<guilabel>KWin Rules</guilabel>. The new rule with its description is listed:"
msgstr ""
"Klõpsuga nupule <guilabel>OK</guilabel> saab minna tagasi <guilabel>KWini "
"reeglite</guilabel> põhiaknasse. Seal on nüüd kirjas uus reegel oma "
"kirjeldusega:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:635
#, no-c-format
msgid "Click <guilabel>OK</guilabel> to close the window."
msgstr "Klõpsa <guilabel>OK</guilabel> akna sulgemiseks."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:636
#, no-c-format
msgid "Done."
msgstr "Valmis."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:639
#, no-c-format
msgid "Application on all Desktops and Handle One Child Window Uniquely"
msgstr "Rakendus kõigil töölaudadel ja ühe alamakna unikaalne kohtlemine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:640
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Except for conversation windows, display &kopete; and its children windows "
"on all desktops and skip the systray and pager. For children conversation "
"windows, treat them as the parent window except show them in systray."
msgstr ""
"&kopete; ja sele alamakende, välja arvatud vestlusaknad, näitamine kõigil "
"töölaudadel, aga mitte süsteemisalves ja töölaudade vahetajas. Vestluse "
"alamakende kohtlemine eellasaknana, aga siiski mittenäitamine süsteemisalves."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:642
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For each attribute, use the <guilabel>Force</guilabel> <link linkend="
"\"parameters\">parameter</link> so it can not be overridden."
msgstr ""
"Kasuta kõigi atribuutide korral <link linkend=\"parameters\">parameetrit</"
"link> <guilabel>Sunnitakse peale</guilabel>, et neid ei saaks tühistada."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:644
#, no-c-format
msgid "In order to implement the above, two rules need to be created:"
msgstr "Ülaltoodu teostamiseks tuleb luua kaks reeglit:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:647
#, no-c-format
msgid "A rule for <guilabel>Kopete Chat</guilabel> and"
msgstr "Reegel <guilabel>Kopete vestlusele</guilabel> ja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:648
#, no-c-format
msgid "A rule for &kopete;"
msgstr "Reegel &kopete;le"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:650
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Kopete Chat</guilabel> rule's matching-criteria is more "
"restrictive than the <emphasis>Kopete</emphasis> rule as it needs to match a "
"specific Window Role: the chat window. Due to <link linkend=\"rule-evaluation"
"\">rule evaluation</link> processing, the <guilabel>Kopete Chat</guilabel> "
"rule must precede the &kopete; rule in the <link linkend=\"kopete-kwin-rule-"
"list\">KWin Rule list for Kopete</link>."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Kopete vestluse</guilabel> reegli sobivuskriteeriumid on "
"piiravamad kui <emphasis>Kopete</emphasis> reeglil, sest see peab vastama "
"konkreetse akna rolliga: vestlusaken. <link linkend=\"rule-evaluation"
"\">Reegli hindamise</link> järjekorra tõttu peab <guilabel>Kopete vestluse</"
"guilabel> reegel <link linkend=\"kopete-kwin-rule-list\">KWini Kopete "
"reeglite loendis</link> eelnema &kopete; reeglile."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:652
#, no-c-format
msgid "Kopete Chat Rule"
msgstr "Kopete vestluse reegel"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:653
#, no-c-format
msgid "Assuming a <guilabel>Kopete Chat</guilabel> window is open:"
msgstr "Eeldame, et <guilabel>Kopete vestluse</guilabel> aken on avatud:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:656
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use <guilabel>Detect Window Properties</guilabel> and select the "
"<guilabel>Kopete Chat</guilabel> window. Check the <guilabel>Window role</"
"guilabel> box to restrict the criteria to chat windows - for additional "
"information see <link linkend=\"window-matching\">window matching</link>:"
msgstr ""
"Kasuta nuppu <guilabel>Akna omaduste tuvastamine</guilabel> ja vali "
"<guilabel>Kopete vestluse</guilabel> aken. Märgi kastike <guilabel>Akna "
"roll</guilabel>, et piirata kriteeriume vestlusakendega (täpsemalt "
"kõneldakse sellest <link linkend=\"window-matching\">akende sobivuse</link> "
"osas):"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:668 index.docbook:713 index.docbook:774 index.docbook:842
#: index.docbook:885 index.docbook:928
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking <guilabel>OK</guilabel> in the previous window back-fills the "
"results in the <guilabel>Window Matching</guilabel> tab. Enter a meaningful "
"text in the <guilabel>Description</guilabel> box:"
msgstr ""
"Klõpsuga nupule <guilabel>OK</guilabel> täidetakse suletud akna põhjal "
"andmed kaardil <guilabel>Akende sobivus</guilabel>. Kirjuta mingi mõistlik "
"tekst väljale <guilabel>Kirjeldus</guilabel>:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:680 index.docbook:725 index.docbook:854 index.docbook:897
#: index.docbook:940
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enable the following attributes:"
msgstr "Lülita sisse järgmised atribuudid:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:692 index.docbook:737 index.docbook:798 index.docbook:866
#: index.docbook:909 index.docbook:952 index.docbook:1005
#, no-c-format
msgid "Click through to complete entry of the rule."
msgstr "Klõpsa OK reegli määramise lõpetamiseks."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:694
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Skip taskbar</guilabel> attribute is set to <guilabel>No</"
"guilabel> to display the window in the taskbar which loosely translates to: "
"<emphasis>no</emphasis> <emphasis>do not</emphasis> <emphasis>skip taskbar</"
"emphasis> <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Face-smile."
"png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject>."
msgstr ""
"Atribuudi <guilabel>Puudub tegumiribalt</guilabel> väärtuseks on "
"<guilabel>Ei</guilabel> akna näitamiseks tegumiribal, sest see kooslus "
"tähendab umbes <emphasis>ei</emphasis>, <emphasis>ära</emphasis> "
"<emphasis>puudu tegumiribalt</emphasis> <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> "
"<imagedata fileref=\"Face-smile.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:697
#, no-c-format
msgid "Kopete Rule"
msgstr "Kopete reegel"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:698
#, no-c-format
msgid "Assuming &kopete; is open:"
msgstr "Eeldame, et &kopete; on avatud:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:701
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use <guilabel>Detect Window Properties</guilabel> and select the &kopete; "
"window. Match only by primary class name so leave the check boxes unchecked "
"- for additional information see <link linkend=\"window-matching\">window "
"matching</link>:"
msgstr ""
"Kasuta nuppu <guilabel>Akna omaduste tuvastamine</guilabel> ja vali &kopete; "
"aken. Sobivuseks kasutame ainult primaarklassi nime, nii et jäta kastikesed "
"märkimata (täpsemalt kõneldakse sellest <link linkend=\"window-matching"
"\">akende sobivuse</link> osas):"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:740
#, no-c-format
msgid "Kopete KWin Rule List"
msgstr "Kopete KWini reegli loend"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:741
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As mentioned, due to <link linkend=\"rule-evaluation\">rule evaluation</"
"link> processing, the <guilabel>Kopete Chat</guilabel> rule must precede the "
"&kopete; rule:"
msgstr ""
"Nagu märgitud, peab <link linkend=\"rule-evaluation\">reeglite hindamise</"
"link> korra tõttu <guilabel>Kopete vestluse</guilabel> reegel seisma "
"&kopete; reeglist eespool:"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:756
#, no-c-format
msgid "Suppress a Window from showing on Pager"
msgstr "Akna mittenäitamine töölaua vahetajas"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:757
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>KNotes</guilabel> currently does not allow for its notes to skip "
"the pager however a rule easily solves this shortcoming."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>KNotes</guilabel> ei võimalda praegu mitte lasta märkmeid töölaua "
"vahetajas näidata, kuid reegliga saab sellest hõlpsasti üle."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:759
#, no-c-format
msgid "Assuming a <emphasis>sticky note</emphasis>' window is available:"
msgstr "Eeldame, et <emphasis>märkmepaberi</emphasis> aken on olemas:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:762
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use <guilabel>Detect Window Properties</guilabel> and select any "
"<emphasis>sticky note</emphasis> window. Match only by primary class name so "
"leave the check boxes unchecked - for additional information see <link "
"linkend=\"window-matching\">window matching</link>:"
msgstr ""
"Kasuta nuppu <guilabel>Akna omaduste tuvastamine</guilabel> ja vali suvaline "
"<emphasis>märkmepaberi</emphasis> aken. Sobivuseks kasutame ainult "
"primaarklassi nime, nii et jäta kastikesed märkimata (täpsemalt kõneldakse "
"sellest <link linkend=\"window-matching\">akende sobivuse</link> osas):"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:786
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enable the <guilabel>Skip Pager</guilabel> attribute with the "
"<guilabel>Force</guilabel> <link linkend=\"parameters\">parameter</link>:"
msgstr ""
"Lülita sisse atribuut <guilabel>Puudub töölaua vahetajalt</guilabel> <link "
"linkend=\"parameters\">parameetriga</link> <guilabel>Sunnitakse peale</"
"guilabel>:"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:801
#, no-c-format
msgid "Force a Window to the Top"
msgstr "Akna sundimine asuma teiste peal"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:802
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To pop an active window to the top, set its <guilabel>Focus stealing "
"prevention</guilabel> attribute to <guilabel>None</guilabel>, typically, in "
"conjunction with the <guilabel>Force</guilabel> <link linkend=\"parameters"
"\">parameter</link>:"
msgstr ""
"Et aktiivne aken oleks teiste peal, tuleb määrata atribuudile "
"<guilabel>Fookuse röövimise vältimine</guilabel> väärtuseks "
"<guilabel>Puudub</guilabel>, reeglina koos <link linkend=\"parameters"
"\">parameetriga</link> <guilabel>Sunnitakse peale</guilabel>:"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:816
#, no-c-format
msgid "Multiple Rules per Application"
msgstr "Mitu reeglit ühele rakendusele"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:817
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<application>Thunderbird</application> has several different child windows. "
"This example:"
msgstr ""
"<application>Thunderbirdil</application> on mitmeid alamaknaid. Selles "
"näites:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:820
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Pin <application>Thunderbird</application>'s main window on "
"<emphasis>Virtual Desktop 1</emphasis> with a specific size and location on "
"the desktop."
msgstr ""
"Kinnistame <application>Thunderbirdi</application> peaakna "
"<emphasis>virtuaalsele töölauale 1</emphasis> konkreetse suuruse ja "
"asukohaga."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:821
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Allow the <application>Thunderbird</application> composer window to reside "
"on any desktop and when activated, force focus and pop it to the top of all "
"windows."
msgstr ""
"Lubame <application>Thunderbirdi</application> kirja koostamise aknal olla "
"suvalisel töölaual ning aktiveerimise korral röövida fookuse ja olla kõige "
"teiste akende peal."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:822
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Pop the <application>Thunderbird</application> reminder to the top and do "
"not give it focus so it isn't inadvertently dismissed."
msgstr ""
"Lubame <application>Thunderbirdi</application> meeldetuletusel olla teiste "
"akende peal ega anna sellele fookust, et seda ei saaks kogemata sulgeda."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:824
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each rule's matching criteria is sufficiently restrictive so their order "
"within the main &kwin; window is not important to affect <link linkend="
"\"rule-evaluation\">rule evaluation</link>."
msgstr ""
"Kõik reegli sobivuse kriteeriumid on piisavalt piiravad, mistõttu nede "
"järjekord &kwin;i reeglite peaaknas ei mõjuta <link linkend=\"rule-evaluation"
"\">reeglite hindamist</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:826
#, no-c-format
msgid "Thunderbird - Main"
msgstr "Thunderbird - peaaken"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:827
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Assuming the <guilabel>Thunderbird Main</guilabel> window is open, sized and "
